description: This Kotlin file defines a singleton object SupabaseConfig that provides access to environment-specific Supabase configuration parameters (URL and key) via utility functions.

methods.name: getSupabaseUrl
methods.description: Retrieves the Supabase URL from environment utilities based on the provided context.

methods.name: getSupabaseKey
methods.description: Retrieves the Supabase key from environment utilities based on the provided context.
